  "message": "Clean up war-stories page: remove unused icons, tighten layout\n\nRemoves 4 unused lucide-react icon imports (Zap, AlertTriangle,\nShield, Activity) that were erroneously added to the import line.\nOnly Skull is actually referenced in the page JSX.\n\nAlso includes linter-applied formatting changes:\n- Responsive header padding (pt-32 pb-16 on mobile, md:pt-44\n  md:pb-20 on desktop) for better mobile viewport use\n- Hero \"Stories.\" accent color changed from text-animate-green\n  to text-red-500 for stronger thematic contrast with the war\n  stories content\n- Animation delay shortened from 1s to 0.4s on the subtitle for\n  snappier perceived load\n- WarStoriesMap wrapped in a container div for group hover context\n- CTA buttons restyled: smaller text (text-sm), uppercase tracking,\n  underscore-separated labels (VIEW_ON_GITHUB, GET_STARTED)\n- Comment casing normalized to uppercase section headers\n- Removed trailing whitespace and blank lines\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
